承受唔到太大風險嘅都可以做後排first-aid<br />\n<br />\n有示威者嘅地方就需要first-aid<br />\n做得幾多得幾多啦<br />\nFirst-aider共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4399115ba147b40b1ef7d5d15a8e3696fe4f462b","tid":1453581,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:04:51.000Z","msg":"TG:firstaid135"},{"pid":"c8bba119b55c2fb9fb1c6c84a6f10f2a2a6c4bbe","tid":1453581,"uid":280725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a3da697e05e4e4bdd418e23078b842c2401bf40","tid":1453581,"uid":283086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b76d9b58a31ceb0673e1153de52df493cfae66a4","tid":1453581,"uid":143269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:47:27.000Z","msg":"我都想知<br />\n<br />\n利申 大學醫療科 未grad 唔知自己夠唔夠資格幫人first aid<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:43:32.000Z","msg":"只要肯肩負起救援標誌同原則就有資格做first-aid<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過要考慮前線first-aiders都會受到安全同被捕風險<br />\n如果承受唔到太大風險嘅都可以做後排first-aid<br />\n<br />\n有示威者嘅地方就需要first-aid<br />\n做得幾多得幾多啦<br />\nFirst-aider共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:21:09.000Z","msg":"係咪一定要有牌先做得first aid?"},{"pid":"bb787b991effebf3b8927896819be40ec0771fd0","tid":1453581,"uid":283086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8bba119b55c2fb9fb1c6c84a6f10f2a2a6c4bbe","tid":1453581,"uid":280725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a3da697e05e4e4bdd418e23078b842c2401bf40","tid":1453581,"uid":283086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b76d9b58a31ceb0673e1153de52df493cfae66a4","tid":1453581,"uid":143269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:47:27.000Z","msg":"我都想知<br />\n<br />\n利申 大學醫療科 未grad 唔知自己夠唔夠資格幫人first aid<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:43:32.000Z","msg":"只要肯肩負起救援標誌同原則就有資格做first-aid<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過要考慮前線first-aiders都會受到安全同被捕風險<br />\n如果承受唔到太大風險嘅都可以做後排first-aid<br />\n<br />\n有示威者嘅地方就需要first-aid<br />\n做得幾多得幾多啦<br />\nFirst-aider共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:21:09.000Z","msg":"係咪一定要有牌先做得first aid?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:54:27.000Z","msg":"建議急救證書要有，最好未過期，始終都係人命。<br />\n<br />\n運用正確急救知識同技巧對傷者進行急救好重要，急救牌係確保傷者得到最適當嘅幫助。<br />\n<br />\n如果急救證書過咗期就盡快續期啦，因為曾經學過first-aid都好，太耐冇運用呢啲急救知識少不免都會生疏。Refresh翻個first-aid 證書再幫更多手足啦。<br />\n<br />\n如果冇急救證書就報St. John或者Red Cross嘅急救課程啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外個人認為沖水沖saline就人人都可以做嘅。特別沖眼注意側頭方向同提醒手足眨眼。<br />\n<br />\n咩崗位都好，主動關心身邊嘅手足啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}